notesStmt.note: Title from title page (f. i recto).
Incipit: La necessità, che là l'vamo di difendersi ... (f. 1r).

msContents.summary: Treatise on the design of fortifications, illustrated with numerous tables and drawings.

supportDesc.extent: 127 leaves : 256 x 197 (195 x 127) mm. bound to 263 x 202 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, i (contemporary paper) + 127 + i (contemporary paper); 1-28, 33-39, [i], 40-45, 29-32, 46-66, [i], 67-143. [i], 144-180, [iv], 182-249, contemporary pagination in ink, upper outer corners; [1-254], modern pagination in pencil, lower outer corners.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in a cursive script by a single hand.

decoDesc.decoNote: Many illustrations showing construction plans which maximize lines of defense, with several fold-out illustrations (p. 39, 56, 66, 124, 143).

history.provenance: Former owners include: Donato Silva (stamp, f. i verso) and Carlo Morbio.
